www.popsugar.com / Wednesday, 14 March 2018 13:30:04

If you know anything about the Kardashians, they seem to be anything but low key, which is why we were surprised when Khloé released her baby registry on Amazon. The mom-to-be teamed up with her sister Kourtney, who has three kids of her own, to create a list of must haves for new moms everywhere. The totally relatable and affordable items include everything from swaddles to bottle heaters and even a breast pump
title: Khloe Kardashian's Amazon Baby Registry Is Worth More Than $6,000: All the Details
